    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Must have met the inclusion criteria for preceding double-blind BID study in
             postherpetic neuralgia

          -  Must have received pregabalin/placebo under double-blind conditions for a minimum of 3
             weeks.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients cannot participate if they experienced a serious adverse event during
             preceding double-blind BID study which was determined to be related to the study
             medication.
      </textblock>
